Description: Provides the shared visual identity for the Circadia Lab R
    ecosystem: colour palettes, ggplot2 theme, and ggplot2 scales. Palettes
    cover qualitative, sequential, and diverging use cases anchored on the
    lab's brand colours. Designed to be used alongside zeitR, slumbR,
    tallieR, and syncR.
